scenes.description: Chloe prepares to show something to the viewers.
Introduction to the 'Sakamata Sports' segment and the first challenge.
Chloe performs the side-to-side jumps challenge.
Chloe reacts to the results and mentions trending #1 on Twitter.
A mysterious video request leads to a chaotic glitch sequence.
Chloe is virtually forced to take off her heavy coat and reveals her outfit.
Introduction to the next sports challenge: the back extension.
